unch and connect to web instances, share links for others to download files, and collaborate through invitations. The best part? It\u0026#39;s completely free if hosted on your hardware, and everything is audited and available in the public domain.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIf you don\u0026#39;t wish to self-host Peergos but have the desire to leave Google, Microsoft, or some other host, Peergos starts from £3 for 300 MB. It\u0026#39;s pretty pricey, which is why I recommend hosting the service yourself from home. The name is pretty cool too. Peergos comes from the Greek word Πύργος (or Pyrgos), which means stronghold or tower. It\u0026#39;s then phonetically spelt and pronounced to showcase its links to the peer-to-peer network architecture.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"446b-40e5-81f2cfdb19c7\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/turn-old-pc-into-a-private-cloud/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"The Nextcloud UI displayed on a Poco M6 Pro, with a PC in the background\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/07/nextcloud-3.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/turn-old-pc-into-a-private-cloud/\" title=\"I turned my old PC into a private cloud - here\u0026#39;s how I did it\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tI turned my old PC into a private cloud - here\u0026#39;s how I did it\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eNextcloud can transform your outdated system into an excellent cloud with robust file-sharing and data backup provisions\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-install-peergos-at-home\"\u003e\n                        How to install Peergos at home\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2094\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Peergos\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-instance-running-hero.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eInstalling Peergos as a self-hosted environment isn\u0026#39;t the easiest. There are apps available for macOS, Linux, and Windows, but these are tailored for connecting to an existing host. You\u0026#39;ll need to run the included Java file to create a server (or pay Peergos to do it for you). I opted to keep things simple and loaded Peergos on a dedicated Windows test system, taking advantage of the vast drive capacities of a connected NAS. Peergos is entirely peer-to-peer, yet is relatively simple to launch and manage. DNS servers and TLS are optional.\u003c/p\u003e        \u003col\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Download \u003ca href=\"https://peergos.net/public/peergos/releases\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ePeergos\u003c/a\u003e for your chosen OS.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Install \u003cstrong\u003eJava\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Install \u003cstrong\u003ePeergos\u003c/strong\u003e.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Run the included \u003cstrong\u003eJava file\u003c/strong\u003e within the Peergos installation.\n                                            \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1734\" height=\"927\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Peergos command line launch\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-command-line-screenshot.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Launch \u003cstrong\u003ePeergos\u003c/strong\u003e and connect to the newly hosted instance using the created token.\n                                            \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                                        \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"3840\" height=\"2088\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Peergos login\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png\" src=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/peergos-account-creation-screenshot.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Create a \u003cstrong\u003epublic account\u003c/strong\u003e with a strong password.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eCompleting these steps will take you to the main dashboard where you can create users, install apps, manage content, and decide which features will be available. There\u0026#39;s also a Docker container for Peergos to capitalize on continued NAS market growth. It\u0026#39;s similar to Nextcloud and some other competing solutions. It\u0026#39;ll be vital, alongside other packages like Immich, in my quest to reduce my reliance on large companies, including Google and Microsoft.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"who-is-peergos-for\"\u003e\n                        Who is Peergos for?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eThis is an interesting question to answer since Peergos relies on the same technologies we enjoy with gaming, file transfers, and other peer-to-peer services. It\u0026#39;s secure and capable in that you can completely bypass the DNS and TLS since you\u0026#39;ll utilize end-to-end encryption. It\u0026#39;s also great for larger file sizes with a limit of around 4 petabytes (PBs) — that\u0026#39;s one million gigabytes (GBs). It\u0026#39;s also good for those who are paranoid (sometimes rightfully so) with current service availability.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eVirtual private networks (VPNs) and other security measures only go so far in protecting your data, especially when moving it between online locations. Peergos has been developed from the ground up to remain an option for those, even should the worst happen and the company fold. So long as you continue running the instance and maintain access for all connected accounts, you can continue sharing news, calendar entries, files, and more.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003ePerformance is pretty good, especially when moving files around internally across the LAN, but even remote connections are pretty rapid, depending on current signal strength and how fast your home upload speeds are. It\u0026#39;s not for everyone and does take a little bit more to get set up and running, but Peergos is worth checking out should you require the additional privacy overhead.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
